; Tests for history.cc: multi-hop price conversion through graph
; Covers: (dijkstra shortest path, price conversion loop)
;         (continue in loop)
;         (return nullopt when u_comm/v_comm not last_target)
;         (price calculation with inversion)

; Three commodities: EUR -> GBP -> $, requiring multi-hop conversion
P 2024/01/01 EUR 0.85 GBP
P 2024/01/01 GBP $1.27

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses  10 EUR
    Assets

; Convert EUR to $ through GBP via dijkstra path
test bal -X '$'
             $-10.80  Assets
              $10.80  Expenses
--------------------
                   0
end test
